# This repo is consumed as a Docker build context (the RedStar `edward` deploy uses
# it as the `ein` named context — for agent-service's Cargo path dependency and the
# wasm32-wasip2 plugin build). Without this, Cargo's target/ (tens of GB) would be
# transferred on every build. Exclude build output and VCS metadata; the Cargo
# sources (crates/, plugins/, eind/, ein/, wit/, Cargo.*) are kept.
target/
.jj/
**/.DS_Store
